@startuml IRouter_removeLiquidityCustom
actor User
participant Router
participant Vault
participant Pool
participant Hooks

== Initiation ==
User -> Router: removeLiquidityCustom(pool, maxBptAmountIn, minAmountsOut, wethIsEth, userData)
note right: User calls Router to remove liquidity with custom logic.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L280-L302

== Vault Unlocking ==
Router -> Vault: unlock(encoded params)
note right: Router encodes params and calls Vault.unlock.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L286-L301

== Remove Liquidity Hook ==
Vault -> Router: removeLiquidityHook(params)
note right: Vault executes Router's hook.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L292-L327

== Remove Liquidity Logic ==
Router -> Vault: removeLiquidity(RemoveLiquidityParams with kind=CUSTOM)
note right: Router calls Vault for custom removal.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L294-L302

alt shouldCallBeforeRemoveLiquidity == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onBeforeRemoveLiquidity(...)
    note right: Optional pre-removal hook.\n**Code Citation**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L234-L242
    Hooks --> Vault: true
end alt

Vault -> Pool: onRemoveLiquidityCustom(router, maxBptAmountIn, minAmountsOutScaled18, balancesLiveScaled18, userData)
note right: Pool computes custom amounts.\n**Code Citation**: IPoolLiquidity.sol#L26-L39
Pool --> Vault: bptAmountIn, amountsOutScaled18, returnData

alt shouldCallAfterRemoveLiquidity == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onAfterRemoveLiquidity(...)
    note right: Optional post-removal hook, may adjust amounts.\n**Code Citation**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L244-L252
    Hooks --> Vault: adjustedAmountsOutRaw
end alt

Vault --> Router: bptAmountIn, amountsOut, returnData

== Token Transfers ==
loop for each token
    alt wethIsEth == true and token == WETH
        Router -> Vault: unwrap WETH and transfer ETH to user
        note right: WETH unwrapped to ETH.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L314-L316
    else
        Router -> Vault: sendTo(token, user, amountsOut[i])
        note right: Token sent to user.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L318-L320
    end alt
end loop

== Finalization ==
Router -> User: bptAmountIn, amountsOut, returnData
note right: Results returned to user.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L302

@enduml